    "name": "Downtown Science (UK)",
    "profile": "We are Downtown Science, residents at Outlaws Yacht Club, The Social, Hyde Park Book Club and regular guests at North Bar, Headrow House, Belgrave Music Hall, Café Belgique (Amsterdam), Sheaf Street/Duke Studios, The Hepworth Gallery, The Hi-fi Club & more. Resident DJ's on Rising Edge & Alto Radio stations. DJ'd with the likes of Luke Una, Alexander Nut, DJ Okapi, Andy Votel, The Mighty Zaf, Mixmaster Morris, Talking Drums and Nicky Siano amongst others and played at the Inner City Electronic Festival and Red Light Radio (Amsterdam)\r\nCatch us in Leeds and beyond playing the best in leftfield disco, afro beats, cosmic jazz, deep house, balearic beats and more.\r\n\r\nContact via\r\n@TheDownScience on Twitter or\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/DowntownScience/ on FB\r\nhttps://www.risingedge.uk/\r\n\r\nDS are: Andy DS / Yose / The Boogie Monster / Mike Ferry / Decknologist",
